title: 157: The Target Haul Episode (November '21 Edition)
itunes:title: The Target Haul Episode (November '21 Edition)
description: In this week’s episode, Lisa and the gang are taste-testing a wide array of finds like soup dumplings, chicken meatballs, Mexican-style corn, a chopped salad kit, watermelon soda, and SO MUCH MORE! Plus, a creamy chicken dip that Lisa thinks might be the best dip she’s ever had! You know what time it is…  Push play, and then when you’re done, head on over to our Foodcast page for a list of all the products mentioned in the episode!
itunes:summary: We darted back to Target and tried 14 items and all but 1 made the cut!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
dc:creator: Lisa Lillien
